,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"行左10分鐘左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/184757_f0aa7c6cc6e7e42069c057ef7bc4462e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F184757_f0aa7c6cc6e7e42069c057ef7bc4462e.jpg&h=21af80b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/25i790V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F25i790V.jpg&h=9864f19a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仆你個街今日真係好熱，忍唔住除左衫山，好彩冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ba7a79a0075c433d2c0677d2722778b112ee05","tid":50313,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:50:06.000Z","msg":"上飛鵝山條樓梯係咪一開始會過個墳先？<br />\n上次同fd行見到個墳就走左<br />\n諗住一陣自己上"},{"pid":"3a33e90cb1e8b7f6e2c96c067572cb2f238ce2d0","tid":50313,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/184435_25a70b17a60dc3426266da17110c2db0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F184435_25a70b17a60dc3426266da17110c2db0.jpg&h=423737b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張都係cap,山路入口，沿路好多絲帶唔怕行錯路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但夜晚行山路？<br />\n上到去有個位要攀過一舊大石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nLihkg無行山撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be32d7f78170d693bd80f4a5b0998bcc2b414401","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"講返帶左咩食糧先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c2r8g31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc2r8g31.jpg&h=f51f4381&s={SIZE}\" />$15美心全麥芝士包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/185456_6eb99487a359205b82ebad29679a319e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F185456_6eb99487a359205b82ebad29679a319e.jpg&h=b9ab98b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蕉一隻free（示意圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/185526_4b7d2a54ed29166c842e80977ec44f38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F185526_4b7d2a54ed29166c842e80977ec44f38.jpg&h=5afddad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n$3 750ml清涼水一枝（示意圖）"},{"pid":"052a2dac4ce2a97cef59ef759a31aa619179732f","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/184435_25a70b17a60dc3426266da17110c2db0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F184435_25a70b17a60dc3426266da17110c2db0.jpg&h=423737b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張都係cap,山路入口，沿路好多絲帶唔怕行錯路</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但夜晚行山路？<br />\n上到去有個位要攀過一舊大石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n <br />\nLihkg無行山撚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係呀我1330開波行，宜家返左屋企啦"},{"pid":"122b41d477c0e8632c1f5fddd248bd4276009d34","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:58:23.000Z","msg":"沖個涼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6aa89cb5d1195171ab94ebe0102d459125cbb4f","tid":50313,"uid":28669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沖個涼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得啦<br />\n仲諗緊點解唔帶頭燈咁顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1e46b09b1b6cdc51f1e88479eb2a5a58b9b69c","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:26:25.000Z","msg":"好繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沿路真係好撚熱又斜，基本上行一陣就要抖下飲水，支水好快得返一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600f35986819067f0fe782e6c0353355eba4f7b5","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>沖個涼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得啦<br />\n仲諗緊點解唔帶頭燈咁顛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有機會都想試夜行，不過真係要搵friend帶，事關小弟唔係成日行山冇咩經驗"},{"pid":"f1b6a1b7fe1e51eb5dc6332c62895ce1941f3bac","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:29:15.000Z","msg":"連登冇人行山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a839aacc61a8a334e4ab1a64a1241bb9412c21ee","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/193058_207f9f19e0ae9c000b50bfd3523af22a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F193058_207f9f19e0ae9c000b50bfd3523af22a.jpg&h=a2c4ae3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行行下會見到呢舊石，跟住轉左（cap 圖）"},{"pid":"600b31aba8e3913a351171ab77682d32bf0b8646","tid":50313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登冇人行山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次我係由寶林行去飛鵝山"},{"pid":"2fddcd1fdcc695a501261fe23c2ef5c22a11b7d2","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登冇人行山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次我係由寶林行去飛鵝山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打果次行左幾耐下次試下果邊上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316fcbdf480614d39927e8b3d4cae6d253cf8a31","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/74Ny80i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F74Ny80i.jpg&h=9ae96c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（cap圖）轉左之後會見到有繩（冇咩用）跟住會平移一小段路"},{"pid":"5c998b35cd63c553198f5e66065113ac65690566","tid":50313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>連登冇人行山？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次我係由寶林行去飛鵝山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打果次行左幾耐下次試下果邊上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寶林-》翠林-》麥理浩徑（唔記得邊條）-》井欄樹-》飛鵝山-》跟住沿路落都經過獅子山入口 最後唔記得去左邊 全程3-4個鐘左右 一開始條路得見到2個鬼佬 去到飛鵝山先多d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8834a7fdc95aff0cf2a0452b219b44319349d02a","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/194236_cba357bfef60c90998b9fda7ceab6916.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F194236_cba357bfef60c90998b9fda7ceab6916.jpg&h=1fa100ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（cap圖）跟住就係撚咁向上爬，呢個位都幾辛苦，斜得黎又要勁曬，除左衫都照出晒水，要係咁抖"},{"pid":"de9d29f462626434b115707a121d4c3c5797a3c2","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/194656_8e43d7e737b42a4278e92fe7a78c2b9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F194656_8e43d7e737b42a4278e92fe7a78c2b9c.jpg&h=a8abc03c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（又係cap圖sorry呢度太熱冇咩影相）見到自殺崖"},{"pid":"50a7243de32c2170ce855c89ff6500217da94b17","tid":50313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"如果巴打鐘意行山路多過石路下次可以上大帽山 佢後半段條山路幾好行 重點係少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88dfabc7e7b679a559d2dc5927f982037d675093","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有 睇緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上次我係由寶林行去飛鵝山</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打果次行左幾耐下次試下果邊上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寶林-》翠林-》麥理浩徑（唔記得邊條）-》井欄樹-》飛鵝山-》跟住沿路落都經過獅子山入口 最後唔記得去左邊 全程3-4個鐘左右 一開始條路得見到2個鬼佬 去到飛鵝山先多d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都行得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一開始都冇咩人呀，過左自殺崖先見到一堆好撚嘈嘅後生仔，唯有快快手過左佢地，但佢地真係好大聲隔成百米都聽到佢地講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a821762d066775e4b43cf6c7fa41dc353a6ef0c1","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果巴打鐘意行山路多過石路下次可以上大帽山 佢後半段條山路幾好行 重點係少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大帽山都冇行過"},{"pid":"e14971355a3f5b84017b1f7542ff633165e366e8","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/202924_d278b324557bb3a13f0597fae0eafeec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F202924_d278b324557bb3a13f0597fae0eafeec.jpg&h=8e7ae845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（2:24pm)自殺崖，叫路人幫手影"},{"pid":"dd44e1cf40c05c6b9126c173d9fd447761e03212","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Of77181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOf77181.jpg&h=d6daab67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(2:39pm)望到山頂發射站"},{"pid":"5b4090d0dcb97d2f42e87ea9c791b13340018fe8","tid":50313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打果次行左幾耐下次試下果邊上先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寶林-》翠林-》麥理浩徑（唔記得邊條）-》井欄樹-》飛鵝山-》跟住沿路落都經過獅子山入口 最後唔記得去左邊 全程3-4個鐘左右 一開始條路得見到2個鬼佬 去到飛鵝山先多d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都行得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一開始都冇咩人呀，過左自殺崖先見到一堆好撚嘈嘅後生仔，唯有快快手過左佢地，但佢地真係好大聲隔成百米都聽到佢地講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獅子山成條路都多人啦 又多賓賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果想睇鬼妹可以去浪茄 好似去左外國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f75c5f2c275c6931d26ad18cf0258823983903a","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:39:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寶林-》翠林-》麥理浩徑（唔記得邊條）-》井欄樹-》飛鵝山-》跟住沿路落都經過獅子山入口 最後唔記得去左邊 全程3-4個鐘左右 一開始條路得見到2個鬼佬 去到飛鵝山先多d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打都行得幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日一開始都冇咩人呀，過左自殺崖先見到一堆好撚嘈嘅後生仔，唯有快快手過左佢地，但佢地真係好大聲隔成百米都聽到佢地講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獅子山成條路都多人啦 又多賓賓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  如果想睇鬼妹可以去浪茄 好似去左外國咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上到獅子山頂有好多鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n浪茄正呀不過淨係去過隔離大浪西露營，果晚煮意粉食同執左啲木黎堆營火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc74895c11b76ed49b69c28264d62ea756744ffc","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Gs562j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Gs562j.jpg&h=107e759d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（2:45pm)發射站隔離有有停機坪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9485GHg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9485GHg.jpg&h=1fe43b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遠望應該係沙咀同麻藍笏果邊"},{"pid":"6aad3ef02c814b843e34437a97105d538d136780","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TwxH590.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTwxH590.jpg&h=6bd6e9aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回望發射站<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/204613_b44030d03b3c2cf54753b9c03f987282.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F204613_b44030d03b3c2cf54753b9c03f987282.jpg&h=ba452f1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一地都係港女草"},{"pid":"1c1cb820f7541a38636e3f21f94822849c58908c","tid":50313,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3y9VHZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3y9VHZ8.jpg&h=9ada7c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4b73b3a05e0d7bf1f1fc3a8f062cec40d2c115","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3BF29n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3BF29n.jpg&h=b053cf61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（3:30pm)冇廣角影唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c41a9ab678a74868bcc59bd583b47b832ec78891","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3y9VHZ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3y9VHZ8.jpg&h=9ada7c5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWA diu好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068264a3cbfc781c709c628ee6433b32ae95e29b","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8YWXC7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8YWXC7s.jpg&h=d4b2dbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遠眺獅子山"},{"pid":"9a76b183c1b59708a91ec785993cd409d76b314c","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/205926_d88ed419207d37b019463fb75ff926e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F205926_d88ed419207d37b019463fb75ff926e6.jpg&h=74882b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個海金黃色好撚靚，可惜影唔到個效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rk53ctZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRk53ctZ.jpg&h=149a70b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3:44pm遠眺大老山氣象站"},{"pid":"bb539d2cef4afd8ad7d82b3ef613f452ffa269ae","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m4D2449.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm4D2449.jpg&h=627d498b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n3:50pm近景，仆街去到呢個位對腳開始抽筋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有食下包抖下，但呢度其實係惡夢嘅開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b198744326cfa83e2943efe11cd2aaa3555782b5","tid":50313,"uid":28387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3BF29n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3BF29n.jpg&h=b053cf61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（3:30pm)冇廣角影唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係攝影撚<br />\n我覺得張相個構圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f900859f4ce0f5250b3a6d11a7a43ff2d51982","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:09:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmF9e6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmF9e6d.jpg&h=5ee01bae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完包又按摩左陣大肶就繼續出發，呢個時候支水已經得返一啖，最衰都係貪輕便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2f0d390bb2ee76fea48f49bdeffb7c783b265c","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:10:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s3BF29n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs3BF29n.jpg&h=b053cf61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（3:30pm)冇廣角影唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係攝影撚<br />\n我覺得張相個構圖好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我見人咁影我咪咁影囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要坐晒係度先影到"},{"pid":"0bc560f1d5a903a25f34e86bce30ad909f437240","tid":50313,"uid":113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"我知你係邊個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f47fa198b882ab9cc0003c7019e26a1bebc6c0","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我知你係邊個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又邊個"},{"pid":"86b3f413548a7d554fd5fd69a6d39ec824f5f24d","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我知你係邊個喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又邊個</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中同？"},{"pid":"cce38eb58807f3b39e607ccbca63c79aa46f9f4b","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/212203_22c489f0c5c995d10e21291927b20262.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F212203_22c489f0c5c995d10e21291927b20262.jpg&h=57f4fd61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌你老母對腳行一陣就抽行一陣就抽咁，如是者行左陣就到左札山道觀景台停車場，直行就沙田坳道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QV90jx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV90jx2.jpg&h=ad699062&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n轉左就落返彩虹，其實原本唸住落彩虹就收皮架啦，咁我見時間徜早就膽粗粗試下經獅子山行埋返屋企（姐直行）"},{"pid":"6fa65700bc7649bd0507a87833c00b0c78dd3f13","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8W7w6B4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8W7w6B4.jpg&h=9a6ec3f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4:30pm 沿住車路行冇咩特別，不過今日5:45就會日落所以痛住都照行，希望日落前上到獅子頂"},{"pid":"4cc306ee38202554735407fbd7f92f07ba400e70","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上飛鵝山條樓梯係咪一開始會過個墳先？<br />\n上次同fd行見到個墳就走左<br />\n諗住一陣自己上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係順利邨落車，直行兩分鐘穿過右手邊停車場就上左清水灣道，沿路路覺眼有墳"},{"pid":"75a3ac830de5f5d43fd491132c660a4087b50529","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上飛鵝山條樓梯係咪一開始會過個墳先？<br />\n上次同fd行見到個墳就走左<br />\n諗住一陣自己上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係順利邨落車，直行兩分鐘穿過右手邊停車場就上左清水灣道，沿路路覺眼有墳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSorry宜家先睇到，一個人小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99269abc1e444b46e752127bc2012d35cf7e849","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214035_530045ce33364e120ef39aa540b444c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214035_530045ce33364e120ef39aa540b444c3.jpg&h=53d30045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4:35<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2H8qB86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2H8qB86.jpg&h=99055463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行多兩步到獅子亭，終於見到有士多，即刻買水飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你老味要十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買完水再向坐係士多出邊堆伯伯問路"},{"pid":"e191aa8ce833e1162f5863ee1fece69965f906a2","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/214811_0d7efe0aea8544a117803d6f508549a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F214811_0d7efe0aea8544a117803d6f508549a1.jpg&h=68a7e6cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3130140.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3130140.jpg&h=621a6550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4:39pm原來入口就係不遠處"},{"pid":"c75dc112bd4ac67e9712c513c874d4788006c67e","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1213054.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1213054.jpg&h=3794442a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5:03pm屌你老味呢500米真心攞命，坡度45度左右，對腳抽撚到仆街，但就到頂冇理由唔上埋佢，重要就日落所以要走住屌咁屌上去"},{"pid":"87e8f4be4ae2fdcb59d369eb0dcc07d59a939ed4","tid":50313,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:56:00.000Z","msg":"夜晚影落去好靚wo 下次都夜晚去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd778984740fb36a5fde0013f60a63e1b01c2e2","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:56:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215502_33014c0d10fd1517838d88d9eb7ff70e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215502_33014c0d10fd1517838d88d9eb7ff70e.jpg&h=f144ace3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aT900ST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaT900ST.jpg&h=def5c25e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5:12pm終於上到黎，但呢個位係獅子尾，要再行多陣先到獅子頭，抖左兩分鐘再出發"},{"pid":"4367b69ed94e2525f0206c6b3c6debd9518b4914","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YD8na72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYD8na72.jpg&h=02cd10a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5:20pm獅子頭+一條女，呢個位勁多人影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215743_04b72592bf3977f1399f12b210d03357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215743_04b72592bf3977f1399f12b210d03357.jpg&h=a40577bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔理啦食隻蕉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90197bae10c5adaf87c06cdc3d7ab7da621f6a0","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:03:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YD8na72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYD8na72.jpg&h=02cd10a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5:20pm獅子頭+一條女，呢個位勁多人影相<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/215743_04b72592bf3977f1399f12b210d03357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F215743_04b72592bf3977f1399f12b210d03357.jpg&h=a40577bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔理啦食隻蕉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢度抖左幾分鐘就要再行，因為落山條路好斜好多石級，冇頭燈都幾煩"},{"pid":"b0e3186b46234df5743beb7081258f35ec75d053","tid":50313,"uid":30038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T14:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\